headline: What Shifts Are Driving a New Narrative for Square Amid Growth and Lending Risks?
summary: Block’s stock is seeing renewed attention as the consensus analyst price target rises modestly, from $87.17 to $88.40. Read on to discover what factors are fueling these changes and how you can stay informed as the narrative around Block continues to evolve.
